Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.63,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:09.05,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:18.73,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:26.82,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.66,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:29.91,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:33.49,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:37.37,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:41.63,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.88,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.55,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}終將指引我們走向所堅信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:57.31,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤誠真心 逐步升溫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:01.15,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無虛情假意 非利益所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:05.90,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真實自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:09.65,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}立於所盼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:13.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}願君側耳
